                    <Footer/>
                    <WebAddress>https://www.msha.gov/support-resources/resources-tools</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Resources / Tools</Header>
                <Paragraph>The MSHA posts mine emergency operations information, miners' resources, and technical resources on its "Resources and Tools" web page.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
