                    <Footer/>
                    <WebAddress>https://www.msha.gov</WebAddress>
                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Spanish</Header>
                <Paragraph>In the top right corner of the MSHA's home page are an Español option and an Inglés option. Using these options, visitors to the website can toggle between content in either language.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
