                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Targeted Inspections</Header>
                <Paragraph>The MSHA conducts targeted inspections each month at mines that merit increased attention and enforcement due to their poor compliance history or particular compliance concerns. Each month's inspection results are posted online.</Paragraph>
